Checklist of the Exhibition
Bimal Banerjee
American, born India 1939
Natural Translpine. 1977. "Origami collage"

Purchase Fund. Plate 32

Houston Conwill (left) and Linda Goode
Bryant (center) at A Book Party for
Contextures, which took place on the same.
day as the opening of Houston Conwill's

Courtesy Sean Kelly, New York. Plate 25

American, born 1947
Ritual. 1982-83. Mixed-media installation

brown boots, and miniatures of a jacket on
a hanger, perfume bottle, Barbie hanger,
baseball cap, umbrella, shopping bag,
fan, screen, carryall, comb, can opener,

Boston fern, Easter cactus, and a palm, 18 x
18 in. (45.7 x 45.7 cm). Collection the artist
The Studio Visit. 1983. Mixed-media instal-
lation with "the artist" (doll of Lieutenant.
Uhura from Star Trek), "the curator" (doll

Barbie wig), and miniatures of an easel, two
